                                    text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry's
                                    standard
                                    dummy text ever since the 1500s</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="avaliacao-modal-alinhamento">
                        <div>
                            <h2 class="avaliação-modal">Avaliação:</h2>
                            <div>
                                <button class="estrela" id="1">☆</button>
                                <button class="estrela2" id="2">☆</button>
                                <button class="estrela3" id="3">☆</button>
                                <button class="estrela4" id="4">☆</button>
